Large frogs are easy and fun to camp with a ranger I do it a lot in the forest giant area.  Here is the key though, have ranger pull with snare, have him snare the frog 4 -5 times, once hes done that, turn pet taunt off and send your pet in.  And at this point you can nuke with impunity.  As long as the ranger initially landed 4 or 5 snares, and occasionally resnares as you are nuking, the mob should never turn on you or your pet.  I just sat on my horse and chained FBOT as the ranger ran the frog back and forth in front of me.  Just need to watch pet on frog enrage.  Other than that its a joke.<br>
