<br>
No actually, the giants near zone in are referred to the &quot;ocean giants or coastal giants&quot; being that there main concentration is on the coast.<br>
<br>
The forest giants are in the area through the underwater tunnel, the area that also has the big beehive thing.  This is where we did frogs, if you come out of the underwater tunnel, and just run straight out to the opposite wall, that is where we kited them.  Back and forth along that wall.  I think there are about 6 or 7 frog spawns over there..<br>
<br>
Hope that helps.<br>
